         <abstract>
            <p>A correction is given for one of Chambers' second-order iteration formulae. It is shown that composition of the secant method with itself exhibits a convergence exponent of 2.414, whereas composition of the iteration function with itself yields an exponent of 2.831.</p>
          </abstract>
